Package: trackr
Type: Package
Title: Track Progress and Forecast Targets for WDI Indicators
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rossana Tatulli
Maintainer: Rossana Tatulli <rtatulli@worldbank.org>
Description: Calculates progress scores and future targets for any WDI indicator of interest. 
    Users can specify their preferred method and parameters to evaluate and project country performance. 
    Depending on the settings, the package returns between two and six data frames summarizing percentile-based and 
    speed-based scores, as well as historical and future indicator trajectories under different assumptions.
